4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge, aiming to build expertise in cybersecurity. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes weekly with a maximum of 16 participants. Students will gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside advanced topics like cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Participants will also learn to implement data loss prevention strategies and understand compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by various institutions. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop